title: Solar Eclipses, near Earth asteroids and the Rings of Saturn - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/10/17
itunes:title: Solar Eclipses, near Earth asteroids and the Rings of Saturn - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 8/10/17
description:
George Noory and space researcher Steve Kates discuss cycles of solar eclipses including the upcoming American Eclipse on August 21, as well as an asteroid that will fly near Earth in October and the end of the mission of the Cassini space probe to the planet Saturn.
